OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,FAn Oscar-nominated producer has joined
OL,7,Fforces with Oxford residents to save
OL,8,Fthe city's iconic Ultimate Picture
OL,9,FPalace (UPP), as the community-owned
OL,10,Fcinema warns it is at a "crunch point"
OL,11,Fover its future.
OL,13,FDame Pippa Harris DBE, the BAFTA-
OL,14,Fwinning producer behind the Oscar-
OL,15,Fnominated film Hamnet, is the first to
OL,16,Fsign a petition urging Oriel College
OL,17,Fto grant the cinema a long-term lease
OL,18,Fextension.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
