PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,FThe filmmaker, who frequented the
OL,7,Fcinema as a teenager, says the venue
OL,8,Finspired her career.
OL,10,F"Big dreams started in that little
OL,11,Fcinema," Dame Pippa said. "I would go
OL,12,Fthere with friends and was mesmerised
OL,13,Fby so many different films and genres
OL,14,Ffrom all over the world... It opened
OL,15,Fmy eyes to an amazing world which I
OL,16,Fknew I wanted to be part of".
OL,18,FThe Grade II listed building on Jeune
OL,19,FStreet is the fourth oldest
OL,20,Findependent cinema in England.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@HO]sD@[OUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
