PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,FWhile its current lease runs until
OL,7,F2037, management says the clock is
OL,8,Falready ticking.
OL,10,FThe building requires urgent
OL,11,Finvestment for "vital repairs,"
OL,12,Fincluding better disabled access,
OL,13,Fimproved sound, and greener energy
OL,14,Fsystems.
OL,16,FWhile the cinema has planning
OL,17,Fpermission and interested funders,
OL,18,Fthese backers require a lease of at
OL,19,Fleast 25 years before they will
OL,20,Frelease the cash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
