PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,FMicaela Tuckwell, CEO of the UPP, says
OL,7,Fthe current 11 years remaining isn't
OL,8,Fenough to secure the building's
OL,9,Fcommercial viability: "We need to be
OL,10,Fable to modernise if we're going to be
OL,11,Fable to keep up with customer demand.
OL,12,FWe want to stay in the beautiful
OL,13,Fcinema that we belong in".
OL,15,FThe uncertainty stems from Oriel
OL,16,FCollege's development plans.
OL,18,FThe cinema sits within the footprint
OL,19,Fof the proposed 'Fifth Quad,' a
OL,20,Fproject designed to provide more
OL,21,Faccommodation for graduate students.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
