PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,FIn a statement to ITV Meridian, Oriel
OL,7,FCollege said: "We are proud of our
OL,8,Fheritage cinema... and are in dialogue
OL,9,Fwith the new managers about how to
OL,10,Fensure it remains open to the wider
OL,11,Fpublic. We have no plans to extend the
OL,12,Flease at this early stage in the
OL,13,Ftenancy".
OL,15,FHowever, supporters fear the loss of
OL,16,Fthe space would be "tragic".
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
