PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,FYasmin Sidhwa, Artistic Director of
OL,7,Fthe Mandala Theatre Company, which
OL,8,Fuses the cinema to showcase work by
OL,9,Fcare-experienced youth, says: "It's a
OL,10,Fplace where we see things that aren't
OL,11,Fshown anywhere else. They support us
OL,12,Fand young people and people in the
OL,13,Fcommunity like no other place".
OL,15,FDespite the national decline in cinema
OL,16,Fattendance, the UPP is thriving, with
OL,17,Fticket sales up 29% last year.
OL,19,FIt remains the only cinema in Oxford
OL,20,Fstill showing films on 35mm celluloid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
