PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773738294
OL,3,CHollywood producer joins battle to
OL,4,Csave historic cinema
OL,6,F"The projection room feels like
OL,7,Fstepping back in time," says Kit
OL,8,FFinnie, the cinema's projectionist.
OL,10,F"It's a really magical space, and you
OL,11,Fcan feel it when you go in there".
OL,13,FAnneliese Dodds, MP for Oxford East,
OL,14,Fbelieves there is a solution that
OL,15,Fsuits everyone: "There's a real win-
OL,16,Fwin here for Oriel College if they can
OL,17,Fwork with the Ultimate Picture Palace.
OL,18,FLots of people locally have put their
OL,19,Fmoney where their heart is... we need
OL,20,Fto keep it going".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@aO]wD@QOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
